data.information:
Per Chelan County Emergency Management on Facebook: Livestock/large animals: Tillicum Riders, 6204 Kimber Road, is accepting large animals and livestock at the Chelan County Fairgrounds & Expo Center in Cashmere.

Please also remember that if you need assistance with domestic or large/livestock animal care, call Animal Care & Control Dispatch at 509-888-7283. The number is available 24/7. Leave a message if no one picks up immediately, and your call will be returned.
The Red Cross shelter at Christ Center Church is now staffed and open.
